   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">CONDITIONS</uicontrol> blocks enable you to configure business logic by defining conditions such as <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">If</uicontrol>, <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Boolean</uicontrol> and <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Loops</uicontrol>. The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">If</uicontrol> blocks enable you to check if the condition passes. The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Boolean</uicontrol> blocks enable you to determine the success criteria of the If statement. The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Loops</uicontrol> blocks enable you to iterate against a list of rows.</p>
